### ========================================
### 4. TENANT 1 (ACME TECH) - SETUP
### ========================================

### Update Tenant 1 Settings - Branding & Bio
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenant-settings
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orgName": "Acme Tech Solutions",
  "orgBio": "Leading enterprise software solutions provider specializing in cloud infrastructure and DevOps consulting. We serve Fortune 500 companies across North America with cutting-edge technology and expert guidance.",
  "primaryColor": "#0066CC",
  "secondaryColor": "#00D9FF",
  "logoUrl": "https://cdn.dribbble.com/users/402324/screenshots/3500966/acme_logo.png",
  "websiteUrl": "https://acme-tech.com"
}

> {%
    client.log("✓ Updated Tenant 1 settings with branding");
%}

### Tenant 1 - Create Custom Field: Industry (text)
POST {{baseUrl}}/custom-fields
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityType": "Customer",
  "key": "industry",
  "label": "Industry",
  "type": "text",
  "required": true,
  "displayInTable": true,
  "config": {
    "maxLength": 100,
    "placeholder": "e.g., Technology, Finance, Healthcare"
  }
}

