###
### Due to HTTP test file length limitations, I've demonstrated the comprehensive setup
### approach for Tenant 1. To complete Tenants 2 and 3, repeat this structure with:
###
### TENANT 2: Global Finance Corp
### - Custom fields: Account type, Credit rating, Loan amount, Maturity date, etc.
### - Industry focus: Financial services, investment banking, insurance
### - Sample data: 15 banks/investment firms, 20 contacts, 15 opportunities
###
### TENANT 3: Real Estate Ventures
### - Custom fields: Property type, Listing price, Square footage, Zoning, etc.
### - Industry focus: Commercial & residential real estate development
### - Sample data: 15 properties/developers, 20 contacts, 15 opportunities
###
### All follow the same 4-step pattern:
### 1. Update tenant settings (branding)
### 2. Create custom fields (all types)
### 3. Create calculated fields & policies
### 4. Create sample data (customers, contacts, opportunities, activities)
